1. Update your system and install necessary dependencies to manage software properties and GPG keys:
sudo apt update && sudo apt install -y gnupg software-properties-common curl

2. Add the HashiCorp GPG key to your system's keyring:
curl -fsSL https://apt.releases.hashicorp.com/gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /usr/share/keyrings/hashicorp-archive-keyring.gpg

3. Add the official HashiCorp repository to your system's APT sources:
echo "deb [arch=$(dpkg --print-architecture) signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/hashicorp-archive-keyring.gpg] https://apt.releases.hashicorp.com $(lsb_release -cs) main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/hashicorp.list

4. Update your package list to include the new repository's package information:
sudo apt update

5. Install Terraform:
sudo apt install terraform

6. Verify the installation:
terraform --version

